statement.p:
          Find the following cardinalities:



|A| when A = \{4,5,6,\ldots,37\}

|A| when A = \{x \in \Z \st -2 \le x \le 100\}



|A \cap B| when A = \{x \in \N \st x \le 20\} and B = \{x \in \N \st x \mbox{ is prime} \}; note that 1 isn't prime.
